name: Care Satin Oil Mask - 200ml
description: A sumptuous, supremely moisturizing mask perfect for dull, dry hair. Use once or twice a week to nourish and treat. After cleansing, towel dry, work through lengths and ends, indulge and rinse thoroughly. If you want to go all out, wrap a warm towel around your head while Satin Oil Mask sinks in. Its rich formula is made with maracuja, baobab and monoï oil and a blend of five essential minerals so your hair is left feeling good and looking great: healthy, soft and shiny. Good for all hair types, this is a moisturizing must-have. name: Care Color Brilliance Mask - 500 ML
description: An intensive caring mask for color-treated tresses. The Color Sealing Complex ensures long-lasting color brilliance, while the moisturizing, restoring formula repairs, protects and strengthens the hair. Features: - Sunflower seed extract nourishes and neutralizes free radicals, which will extend the longevity of your color - Silk proteins deeply moisturize, nourish and add luminous shine - Protective barrier around each strand, which locks pigments in - UVA and UVB filters block out the sun’s rays to keep your color from fading How to use: - Use once a week after shampoo instead of your conditioner - Apply to lengths and ends and indulge for 3 to 5 minutes
